---

<section class="experience" id="experience">
	<h2 class="heading">Experience</h2>
	<div class="experience-container">
		<div class="experience-box">
			<div class="experience-icon">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i>
			</div>
			<h3>Web Development Internship</h3>
			<p>Assisted in developing web applications and gained hands-on experience in software development. Worked with modern frameworks and collaborated with senior developers.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="experience-box">
			<div class="experience-icon">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i>
			</div>
			<h3>Freelance Graphic Designer</h3>
			<p>Created websites for small businesses and individuals, enhancing my skills in web design and development. Managed client relationships and delivered projects on time.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.experience {
		background: #F5F0E8;
		padding: 3rem 0;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.experience::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background-image: 
			url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noiseFilter'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.8' numOctaves='4' result='noise' seed='2' /%3E%3CfeColorMatrix in='noise' type='saturate' values='0'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100' height='100' fill='%23000000' filter='url(%23noiseFilter)' opacity='0.15'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
		background-size: 100px 100px;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
		mix-blend-mode: overlay;
	}

	.experience-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.experience-box {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 24px;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
		border: 1px solid rgba(163, 29, 29, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}

	.experience-box:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		border-color: rgba(163, 29, 29, 0.2);
	}

	.experience-icon {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A31D1D 0%, #8B1515 100%);
		border-radius: 20px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: white;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(163, 29, 29, 0.3);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-radius 0.3s ease;
	}

	.experience-box:hover .experience-icon {
		transform: scale(1.1) rotate(8deg);
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.experience-box h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		color: #A31D1D;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.experience-box p {
		color: #555;
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.experience .heading {
		color: #4A1215;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		font-style: italic;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.experience .heading span {
		-webkit-text-fill-color: #FEF9E1;
		color: #FEF9E1;
	}
</style>
